latestPosts.caption:
Launch Night of ATM Members Bar hosted by Yours Truly & my Buddy Davina Thacker. 

Pass Code Hospitality, a leading boutique firm in India’s F&B industry, known for its acclaimed brands like PCO, Ping’s, SAZ, Mister Merchant’s, and Jamun, has  launched *ATM Members Bar* in Kolkata, an exclusive private members’ club located in the luxurious heritage building, 1910 Galleria on Camac Street, Kolkata. ATM offers personalized butler services, curated menus and experiences, specialty craft cocktails, fine wines, premium cigars, exclusive tastings and musical performances. Designed as a premier supper club, it aims to foster professional connections, cultural pursuits and intellectual discourse in a refined, intimate setting, complete with live music performances to elevate every evening. 

The Only Premium Cocktail and Cigar Bar in Kolkata. 

Kudos to Rakshay ,Yogesh , Chef Piku & Radhika for bringing this Amazing Members  Supper Club To Kolkata.
